name: Global X Equal Weight Canadian Insurance Index ETF
longDescription: SAFE uses the Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Insurance Index as its Underlying Index. The Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Insurance Index includes the largest TSX-listed securities of Canadian insurance companies. Holding companies are ineligible for inclusion. Constituents are subject to minimum market capitalization and liquidity screens.
fulldescription: SAFE uses the Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Insurance Index as its Underlying Index. The Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Insurance Index includes the largest TSX-listed securities of Canadian insurance companies. Holding companies are ineligible for inclusion.
